            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="size-chart-note">
            <strong>How to Measure</strong>
            Use a soft measuring tape around the fullest part of your chest, natural waistline, and hips. If between sizes, we recommend sizing up for optimal comfort.
          </div>
        </div>

